    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers a refined driving experience that exceeds standard expectations for its class. Every system has been thoroughly vetted to ensure continued performance and long-term reliability. This offering combines sophisticated styling with proven durability, providing exceptional value for those who prioritize professional upkeep and structural excellence.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It's perfect for someone looking for a reliable, smooth journey without that brand-new price tag. It\u2019s clean, runs great, and is totally ready to hit the road with you today! Come take a look\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a 2008 Porsche Cayman S, a pinnacle of mid-engine engineering. This example features the 3.4L M97.21 flat-six powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus, delivering a broad torque curve and a 7,200 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers short-throw precision, paired with a chassis that utilizes MacPherson strut suspension and Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for variable damping. Braking is handled by four-piston aluminum monoblock calipers clamping cross-drilled, vented rotors. The vehicle exhibits excellent torsional rigidity and a neutral handling profile due to its low polar moment of inertia. Recent service includes a fresh clutch slave cylinder and a comprehensive cooling system flush. Ideal for the purist seeking a mechanically honest, high-performance platform.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition, ready for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine with only minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the premium upholstery shows minimal wear, and all electronic features\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, it is sound, having undergone regular, documented servicing. It offers a smooth, quiet ride and robust performance, making it a reliable and stylish choice for any driver who appreciates a car that has been treated with genuine care.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and safety. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, this vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning professional. We invite you to experience the superior handling and reliability that define this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. The engine runs like a dream, and the interior is still looking sharp and cozy. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner! If you're looking for a dependable car that still has tons of life left in it, this is the one. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it or take it for a quick spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54B32 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features a 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including documented rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis is sorted with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the factory-spec limited-slip differential translates torque effectively to the tarmac. While showing honest patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust and optimized for performance-oriented driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
